# 2️⃣ Model Relationships

## Post Model

app/Models/Post.php

```php
public function categories()
{
    return $this->belongsToMany(Category::class);
}
```

---

## Category Model

app/Models/Category.php

```php
public function posts()
{
    return $this->belongsToMany(Post::class);
}
```

