# 4️⃣ Store Method

```php
public function store(Request $request)
{
    $post = Post::create([
        'title'=>$request->title,
        'description'=>$request->description,
        'user_id'=>auth()->id()
    ]);

    $post->categories()->attach($request->categories);

    return redirect()->route('posts.index');
}
```

